-- Insert "Makan di Pantai" story
  '["Hari Sabtu siang. Vlad lagi di rumah, bosen banget. Dia chat temennya, Adi.","\"Eh Adi, lagi ngapain? Hari ini bebas gak?\" \"Lagi di rumah aja. Males banget, gak ada yang seru. Kenapa?\" \"Mau ke mana gitu gak? Bosen banget nih di rumah. Kita pergi bareng yuk.\"","\"Boleh! Mau ngapain? Ke pantai? Ke mall?\" \"Gimana kalau kita makan dulu? Perut laper banget. Terus habis makan baru pikirin mau ke mana.\"","\"Ide bagus! Resto apa yang enak di daerah sini? Aku baru pindah, belum tau banyak tempat.\" \"Ada warung seafood deket pantai, temen aku bilang enak banget. Belum pernah ke sana sih, tapi mau coba.\"","\"Sip, deal. Kapan ketemu?\" \"Sekarang aja! Kamu bisa jemput aku gak? Motor aku lagi dipinjem temen.\" \"Bisa dong. Bentar ya, aku ganti baju dulu. Lima menit.\" \"Oke, aku tunggu di depan.\"","Lima belas menit kemudian. Vlad masih nunggu. \"Adi selalu telat. Emang gitu orangnya.\" Akhirnya Adi datang naik motor.","\"Sori aku telat! Tadi gak bisa cari kunci motornya. Ternyata di dalam tas.\" \"Kan udah aku bilang, taro kunci di tempat yang sama setiap hari. Biar gak lupa.\" \"Iya iya, maaf ya. Yuk pergi, nanti warungnya penuh.\"","Mereka naik motor berdua ke arah pantai. Jalannya lumayan rame, tapi gak macet. \"Jauh gak tempatnya?\" \"Gak, deket kok. Sekitar sepuluh menit dari sini.\"","\"Oh, gampang. Eh, kamu denger gak? Katanya ada festival musik nanti malam di Canggu.\" \"Serius nih? Tiketnya berapa?\" \"Aku gak tau, cek dulu nanti ya.\"","Mereka sampe di warung seafood. Tempatnya deket banget sama pantai. Ada banyak orang udah duduk di sana. \"Wah, rame banget. Mudah-mudahan masih ada tempat.\"","\"Halo! Dua orang ya? Masuk aja, masih ada meja di belakang.\" \"Makasih! Tempatnya enak banget ya, bisa lihat pantai dari sini.\"","\"Mau pesen apa? Ini menunya.\" \"Hmm, banyak banget pilihannya. Kamu mau pesen apa?\" \"Aku mau ikan bakar sama nasi putih. Sama es jeruk satu.\" \"Aku juga mau ikan bakar deh. Tapi yang pedas. Tambah pedas ya.\"","\"Siap. Tunggu sebentar ya, sekitar dua puluh menit.\" \"Lama juga ya.\" \"Santai aja, kita ngobrol dulu sambil nunggu.\"","Mereka ngobrol tentang banyak hal. Kerjaan, rencana, kehidupan di Bali. \"Eh, kamu masih bikin aplikasi itu? Yang buat belajar bahasa?\" \"Iya, masih. Belum selesai sih, ribet banget. Tapi hampir selesai.\"","\"Keren banget sih. Aku pengen bisa bikin kayak gitu juga, tapi susah banget kayaknya.\" \"Gampang kok, kalau udah terbiasa. Aku bisa ajarin kamu kalau mau.\" \"Beneran? Ajarin aku dong! Kapan bisa mulai?\" \"Minggu depan aja. Sekarang santai dulu.\"","Makanannya datang. Bau-nya wangi banget. \"Wah, lihat itu! Gede banget ikannya.\" \"Cium bau apa nih... wangi banget. Aku gak sabar.\"","Mereka langsung makan. Vlad coba ikan bakarnya. \"Ya ampun. Enak banget. Rasanya enak banget, kayak... aku gak bisa jelasin deh. Coba deh, coba.\"","\"Hmm... iya, bener banget. Paling enak sih ini. Dan pedasnya pas — gak terlalu pedas, gak kurang juga.\" \"Makan sambil lihat pantai kayak gini... asik banget deh.\"","\"Bener. Kenapa gak dari dulu kita ke sini ya?\" \"Aku gak tau, aku lupa siapa yang kasih tau aku soal tempat ini. Tapi makanya sekarang kita harus sering ke sini.\"","\"Setuju. Eh, mau tambah lagi gak? Aku masih laper sedikit.\" \"Aku udah cukup sih. Tapi pesen aja kalau kamu mau.\" \"Oke, aku pesen cumi goreng satu lagi ya.\" \"Mau minum lagi?\"","\"Mau kopi gak, Di? Kopinya enak gak di sini?\" \"Kopinya enak, tapi agak pahit. Mau dikasih gula?\" \"Dikit aja gulanya. Kurangin gulanya ya, aku gak suka terlalu manis.\" \"Aku es teh manis aja.\"","Habis makan, Vlad manggil waiter-nya. \"Mau bayar ya. Totalnya berapa?\" \"Bentar ya, aku itung dulu... Seratus lima puluh ribu semua.\"","\"Lumayan juga ya. Siapa yang bayar?\" \"Gantian. Aku bayarin kali ini, kamu yang bayar nanti malam di festival.\" \"Haha, oke, deal. Makasih ya!\"","\"Sama-sama. Eh, kita ke pantai dulu yuk sebelum pulang. Deket banget dari sini.\" Mereka jalan kaki ke pantai. Pantainya bagus banget — pasirnya putih, ombaknya tenang.","\"Cantik banget pantainya. Gila, kenapa aku baru tau tempat ini?\" \"Karena kamu baru pindah! Masih banyak tempat yang belum kamu tau di Bali.\"","\"Bener sih. Eh foto yuk! Matahari-nya bagus banget sekarang.\" \"Foto bareng yuk. Kirim ke aku ya nanti.\" Mereka foto-foto di pantai. Anginnya kencang, tapi enak — seger.","\"Eh, udah sore nih. Kamu mau langsung ke festival nanti malam, atau pulang dulu?\" \"Pulang dulu deh, mau mandi sama ganti baju. Ketemu di sana aja nanti malam.\"","\"Oke. Jam berapa?\" \"Sekitar jam delapan. Jangan telat ya!\" \"Haha, iya iya. Pasti datang kok. Chat aku aja kalau udah sampe.\"","\"Sip. Sampai nanti malam!\" \"Sampai nanti!\" Vlad naik motor Adi balik ke rumah. Hari ini belum selesai — nanti malam pasti seru banget."]'::jsonb,
  '["Saturday afternoon. Vlad is at home, so bored. He texts his friend, Adi.","\"Hey Adi, what are you doing? Are you free today?\" \"Just at home. So lazy, nothing fun going on. Why?\" \"Wanna go somewhere? So bored at home. Let''s go together.\"","\"Sure! What do you wanna do? Beach? Mall?\" \"How about we eat first? Stomach is super hungry. Then after eating we figure out where to go.\"","\"Good idea! What restaurant is good around here? I just moved, don''t know many places yet.\" \"There''s a seafood warung near the beach, my friend said it''s really good. Haven''t been there yet, but I wanna try.\"","\"Great, deal. When do we meet?\" \"Right now! Can you pick me up? My motorbike is being borrowed by a friend.\" \"Of course. One moment, let me change clothes first. Five minutes.\" \"Okay, I''ll wait out front.\"","Fifteen minutes later. Vlad is still waiting. \"Adi is always late. That''s just how he is.\" Finally Adi arrives on his motorbike.","\"Sorry I''m late! Couldn''t find my motorbike key. Turns out it was in my bag.\" \"I already told you, put the key in the same place every day. So you don''t forget.\" \"Yeah yeah, sorry. Let''s go, or the warung will be full.\"","They ride the motorbike together toward the beach. The road is fairly busy, but not jammed. \"Is the place far?\" \"No, it''s close. About ten minutes from here.\"","\"Oh, easy. Hey, did you hear? Apparently there''s a music festival tonight in Canggu.\" \"Are you serious? How much are the tickets?\" \"I don''t know, let me check later.\"","They arrive at the seafood warung. The place is really close to the beach. There are lots of people already sitting there. \"Wow, so crowded. Hopefully there''s still a spot.\"","\"Hello! Two people? Just come in, there''s still a table in the back.\" \"Thanks! The place is so nice, you can see the beach from here.\"","\"What do you want to order? Here''s the menu.\" \"Hmm, so many choices. What are you ordering?\" \"I want grilled fish with white rice. And one iced orange juice.\" \"I''ll also have the grilled fish. But the spicy one. Extra spicy please.\"","\"Got it. Wait a moment, about twenty minutes.\" \"That''s quite a while.\" \"Just relax, let''s chat while we wait.\"","They chat about many things. Work, plans, life in Bali. \"Hey, are you still making that app? The one for learning languages?\" \"Yeah, still am. Not done yet, it''s so complicated. But almost done.\"","\"That''s so cool. I wish I could make stuff like that too, but it seems so hard.\" \"It''s easy, once you''re used to it. I can teach you if you want.\" \"Really? Teach me please! When can we start?\" \"Next week. For now just relax.\"","The food arrives. The smell is so good. \"Wow, look at that! The fish is huge.\" \"Smell that... smells so good. I can''t wait.\"","They immediately start eating. Vlad tries the grilled fish. \"Oh my. So good. The taste is so good, it''s like... I can''t explain it. Try it, try it.\"","\"Hmm... yeah, so true. This is the best honestly. And the spice level is perfect — not too spicy, not too little either.\" \"Eating while looking at the beach like this... so enjoyable.\"","\"True. Why didn''t we come here sooner?\" \"I don''t know, I forgot who told me about this place. But that''s why we should come here often now.\"","\"Agreed. Hey, want to add more? I''m still a little hungry.\" \"I''ve had enough. But order if you want.\" \"Okay, I''ll order one more fried squid.\" \"Want more drinks?\"","\"Want coffee, Di? Is the coffee good here?\" \"The coffee is good, but a bit bitter. Want sugar added?\" \"Just a little sugar. Reduce the sugar, I don''t like it too sweet.\" \"I''ll just have sweet iced tea.\"","After eating, Vlad calls the waiter over. \"I''d like to pay. What''s the total?\" \"One moment, let me calculate... One hundred and fifty thousand total.\"","\"That''s not bad. Who''s paying?\" \"We take turns. I''ll pay this time, you pay tonight at the festival.\" \"Haha, okay, deal. Thanks!\"","\"You''re welcome. Hey, let''s go to the beach first before heading home. It''s really close from here.\" They walk to the beach. The beach is so nice — white sand, calm waves.","\"The beach is so beautiful. Crazy, why am I only just finding out about this place?\" \"Because you just moved! There are still so many places you don''t know in Bali.\"","\"True. Hey let''s take a photo! The sun is really nice right now.\" \"Let''s take a photo together. Send it to me later okay.\" They take photos at the beach. The wind is strong, but nice — refreshing.","\"Hey, it''s already late afternoon. Do you want to go straight to the festival tonight, or go home first?\" \"Go home first, I want to shower and change clothes. Let''s just meet there tonight.\"","\"Okay. What time?\" \"Around eight o''clock. Don''t be late!\" \"Haha, yeah yeah. I''ll definitely be there. Just text me when you''ve arrived.\"","\"Great. See you tonight!\" \"See you later!\" Vlad catches a ride on Adi''s motorbike back home. The day isn''t over yet — tonight is definitely going to be so fun."]'::jsonb,
  'd3d205dd-98df-481d-bf3f-b4d11b3981f1');

